@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

interface Prototype {
  +Clone(): Prototype
}

class ConcretePrototype {
  -state: string
  -items: List<string>
  +Clone(): Prototype
}

class Client {
  +Operation(): void
}

Prototype <|.. ConcretePrototype
Client --> Prototype : uses

note right of ConcretePrototype
Clone() có thể là shallow copy,
deep copy hoặc copy có chọn lọc.
end note
@enduml
